metadata.name: Eternal Dance
metadata.description:
Here you see a hypnotizing dance of swallows spinning in an eternal circle of modernity vs. tradition.

These  are one of my favorite birds, who bring summer and joy to our lives. Also they leave us all alone during autumn until next time. 

Tools: Oil-Pastels, Paper, Photoshop

Mint Size: 3168x2832 px

Primary market collectors can request the Physical painting: 420x297mm on 160gsm paper
